<TITLE>Organization Trends (Index) -- CRC</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/crc/images/bg.gif">
<a href="/crc/images/sidebar.map"><img src="/crc/images/sidebar.gif" alt="Navigation Bar" border="0" align="left" ISMAP></a>
<ul>
<center>
<img src="/crc/images/hdr-ot.gif" alt="Organization Trends">
</center>
<P>
Capital's flagship monthly offers detailed documentary information on advocacy groups, along with the political and financial alliances they deploy to shape the public policy debate.  As a result, journalists, grant-makers and elected officials increasingly rely on <i>OT</i> to provide background information on advocacy groups as new issues emerge on the Washington agenda.
