<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/crc/images/bg.gif">
<a href="/crc/images/sidebar.map"><img src="/crc/images/sidebar.gif" alt="Navigation Bar" border="0" align="left" ISMAP></a>
<ul>
<center>
<img src="/crc/images/hdr-ap.gif" alt="Alternatives in Philanthropy">
</center>
<P>
Capital's monthly newsletter devoted to offering fresh perspectives on prevailing trends and current issues in the philanthropic arena. <i>AP</i> offers important investigative reports and discussions of broad issues in philanthropy.
