<li>The Education Reform Movement: <a href="/crc/ap/ap1-96.html">An Interview with Jeanne Allen</a>, President of the Center for Education Reform
<P>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt><b>December, 1995</b>
<dd><li><a href="/crc/ap/ap-1295.html">From Foster Care to Adoption</a> An Interview with Conna Craig
<P>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt><b>November, 1995</b>
