<A HREF="CostsofInnovation.html"><img Hspace= 6 align= absmiddle  border value =1 WIDTH=33 HEIGHT=22 src= "ForwardArrow.gif"><font color ="#006699" size =2><B><I>Costs of Innovation in the Commons</B></I></FONT></A>
