http://www.empower.org:80/free/ST94/Chlorine94.html 204.71.237.79 19970209223613 text/html 7225
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:36:57 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:16:03 GMT
Content-length: 7042
Content-type: text/html
