http://www.empower.org:80/free/ST94/Biking94.html 204.71.237.79 19970209223655 text/html 7145
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:37:41 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:15:58 GMT
Content-length: 6962
