http://www.empower.org:80/free/ST94/ITQ94.html 204.71.237.79 19970209223744 text/html 7008
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:38:26 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:17:28 GMT
