http://www.empower.org:80/free/ST93/TrustFunds93.html 204.71.237.79 19970209224004 text/html 6562
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:40:48 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:34 GMT
Content-length: 6379
