HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:41:12 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:09 GMT
Content-length: 6323
Content-type: text/html
