FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Yet another new sitcom with a standup comedian at the helm, the 
show revolves around the lives of a personnel manager and his 
friends as they face life in the '90s.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary: </FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook">Despite 
the show's early evening timeslot, <I>Drew Carey</I> dabbles in 
a variety of adult issues, featuring lengthy references to premarital 
sex and occasional objectionable language (&quot;bite me,&quot; 
&quot;ass&quot;).</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="ellen"></a> 
