<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Starring comedienne Ellen DeGeneres as the owner of a bookstore, 
the sitcom highlights the relationships between the protagonist, 
her family, and her friends.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
<I>Ellen</I> frequently introduces sex as a main topic of conversation 
among the characters. Premarital sex and adultery are treated 
casually. </FONT> 
<P> 
 
