<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background: </FONT></B><I><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook">ER</FONT></I><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
focuses on the emergency-room personnel of a Chicago hospital.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Except for an evenhanded argument over abortion last season, the 
doctors and nurses eschew social commentary. Pre- and extramarital 
sex is fairly frequent, though, and the surgery scenes are often 
quite graphic.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="matters"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fgreen.gif"  alt="Green Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
Schoolbook">Family Matters</FONT></B></I> 
<P> 
<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">(ABC/comedy)</FONT> 
<P> 
<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Friday 8 PM </FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
This veteran sitcom focuses on the interactions among the Winslow 
family members.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
The anchor of ABC's Friday- night lineup -- dubbed &quot;TGIF&quot; 
by the network -- <I>Family Matters</I> promotes a respect for 
parental authority, premarital celibacy, and the merits of a happy 
marriage.</FONT> 
<P> 
<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook"> Public service announcements 
have been used to promote organ donor programs and denounce violence 
in schools.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="timeout"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
Schoolbook">First Time Out</FONT></B></I> 
