Despite the characters' conflicting viewpoints, <I>Hudson</I> 
<I>Street</I> promotes chastity and law and order. In recent episodes, 
however, this virtuous stand was mocked by some series regulars.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="inthehouse"></a> 
