<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Humor ensues when a former professional football star takes on 
a job as a nanny, assisting a single mother of two.  </FONT> 
 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Divorce is not glamorized, and the children's parents work in 
tandem to ensure they have the benefits of both a mother and a 
father. However, the athlete alludes to having a loose lifestyle 
and, occasionally, suggestive situations diminish the show's pro-family 
attributes.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="jag"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
