<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
An action series focusing on a JAG -- Judge Advocate General, 
a Navy lawyer -- and his investigations of wrongdoing within his 
branch of the service.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
A fall 1995 premiere, <I>JAG</I> has thus far been sup-portive 
of the military, though it has emphasized that those in authority 
are impeding the suc-cess of women in the armed services. Parents 
may find <I>JAG</I>'s salty language (&quot;bitch,&quot; &quot;bastard&quot;) 
inappropriate for this timeslot.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
