FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Based on the novel and the feature film, and set in the South, 
<I>The Client</I> features a recovering alcoholic who provides 
legal representation for children.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
The show denounces racial bigotry. Positive portrayals of some 
in law enforcement offset <I>The Client</I>'s somewhat derisive 
characterizations of a judicial process unduly influenced by the 
good ol' boy system.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="johnl"></a> 
