<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Larroquette stars as a recovering alcoholic working as the manager 
of a St. Louis bus station. </FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
This sitcom has slammed those who rashly blame racism for their 
shortcomings. <I>Larroquette</I> has alternately slammed, then 
supported, the religious. Although devoid of steamy scenarios, 
the series has decidedly permissive views on premarital sex.</FONT> 
 
 
<P> 
