FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
<I>Live Shot</I> attempts to expose viewers to the realities of 
 working in a Los Angeles television newsroom.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Using explicit scenarios, <I>Live Shot</I> deals with adult material 
including homosexuality and sex; dorsal nudity is also featured. 
Moreover, the show's primary advocate of traditional values is 
routinely portrayed as a fool.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="single"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
