uses her knowledge of criminal behavior to help police find the 
culprit.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary: </FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook">This 
long-running CBS staple is essentially free from any explicit 
sexual content or vulgarity.</FONT> 
 
 
<P> 
