FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
For mature viewing audiences only, this drama's storylines feature 
sex, ribald language, and dorsal nudity. </FONT> 
<P> 
<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Although premarital sex 
is addressed, the show is free of explicit sex scenes.</FONT> 
 
