FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
While most storylines focus on inter-office antics, <I>Murphy</I> 
has thematically glorified illegitimacy and given a thumbs-up 
to premarital sex. Dialogue has slammed the religious and criticized 
proponents of family values. </FONT> 
 
<P> 
