FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
Despite their opposing ideological viewpoints, the title characters 
enter into a marriage of convenience, setting the stage for conflict.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
<I>Ned &amp; Stacey</I> depicts both sides of political and social 
issues honestly, but advances a cynical view of marriage. The 
title characters have a platonic relationship but engage in sex 
with other partners.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="newsradio"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
