FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
<I>NewsRadio</I> features the quirky employees of an all-news 
radio station in New York.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
The series' focus is on the personal lives of the characters, 
which in practice means a lot of sexual references: two characters 
who are having a clandestine affair frequently discuss the physical 
aspects of their relationship.</FONT> 
 
<P> 
<a name="nynews"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
