<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Background:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
A team of newspaper reporters and editors discover the disasters 
and triumphs within New York City.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
<I>New York News</I> has sanctioned premarital sex and adultery, 
and instances of gratuitous violence and foul language have aired. 
Content is not as explicit, and does not mimic <I>NYPD Blue-</I>esque 
dramas in pushing the envelope of network standards. </FONT> 
 
 
<P> 
<a name="undercover"></a> 
<img src="/mrc/images/fyellow.gif"  alt="Yellow Light"><I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
Schoolbook">New York Undercover</FONT></B></I><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="Century 
Schoolbook"> 
</FONT></B> 
<P> 
