FACE="Century Schoolbook">Showcasing 
a strong family unit, the weekly plots concentrate on the relationship 
between four children and their parents.</FONT> 
<P> 
<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
The lead characters' tough-love parenting has been portrayed in 
a positive light; the sitcom's themes thus far have been geared 
toward the strength of family and advocating individual responsibility.</FONT> 
 
