HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:49:30 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 09-Oct-96 19:35:25 GMT
Content-length: 4451
Content-type: text/html
